# Tech Manager OS — Structure Reference

## Purpose

A personal operating system for an engineering manager or tech lead. Manages 1-on-1s, team feedback, company initiatives, career development, and meeting notes — all as Markdown files in Obsidian with Git version control.

Designed for someone who:
- Manages a team across one or more companies/clients
- Runs recurring 1-on-1s and structured feedback cycles
- Participates in company-wide and cross-team initiatives
- Wants a durable, portable, plain-text system that survives tool changes

